{
  "stem": "14810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew it's the Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't hide everything from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They send-- we sensed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was in middle-- I think it was a Tuesday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- they throw us-- they gave us each one piece of bread, one half of one portion of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said it wouldn't take long, and-- and fortunately for us, we could take out blankets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At Buna, we had blankets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody had one blanket.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had my utensils.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, we had this utensil for soup and a cup for coffee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we-- we could take these with this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The reason I said that-- I will tell you later why this helped us a lot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we marched the whole night-- that's from Auschwitz to Gliwice, which was almost 70 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And here the snow was about two feet tall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was bitter cold, and here we had always wooden shoes or [INAUDIBLE] shoes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was almost impossible to walk, and we had to run, literally run, because we could hear-- at night, you could see from the heavy artillery, from the muzzles, you could see the-- the bullets, the fired artillery.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They could have been maybe 20 or 30 miles away from us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the SS men, they just said run.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The first few hours was fair, but then most people got tired.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They couldn't-- couldn't run, so a lot of people just dropped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And anybody who dropped, if you couldn't make it, you could hear the pistol shots every few minutes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It must have been by the hundreds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Literally, the whole road was littered with-- with bodies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was walking with my brother all this time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember it was already middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was maybe about six or seven hours, and we were all exhausted.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
